319
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:29,039
Mom.

320
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:30,720
Mom.

321
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,559
It's not like this.

322
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:36,200
It's not like this.

323
