332
00:24:52,759 --> 00:24:53,480
Lan!

333
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:54,119
Lan!

334
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,319
Mom! Mom!

335
00:24:55,319 --> 00:24:55,920
Lan.

336
