Remember.

340
00:25:04,039 --> 00:25:05,400
Better to be a wife in a humble home

341
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:05,960
Go, Mom...

342
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:08,200
than a concubine in a great mansion.

343
00:25:08,279 --> 00:25:09,319
Mom.

344
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:47,279
Mom.

345
00:25:55,680 --> 00:25:56,720
Jinzhao.

346
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,000
My poor...

347
00:26:01,319 --> 00:26:02,440
Grandmother! Grandmother!

348
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,079
Grandmother!

349
00:26:03,079 --> 00:26:03,559
Madam Ji! Grandmother!

350
00:26:03,559 --> 00:26:04,480
Grandmother, hurry!

351
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:06,279
Fetch the physician, quickly!

352
00:26:10,799 --> 00:26:11,799
This modification,

353
