is that it holds very few needles,

357
00:26:17,799 --> 00:26:18,759
and has a short range.

358
00:26:19,119 --> 00:26:19,720
This one advantage,

359
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,160
of being hard to detect,

360
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,440
trumps everything else.

361
00:26:24,519 --> 00:26:25,759
What are you tinkering with here again.

362
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:28,559
My Lady.

363
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:29,640
Mr. Xiao.

364
