399
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,359
What more do I have to worry about.

400
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,119
Miss.

401
00:28:40,599 --> 00:28:41,359
It is dawn.

402
00:28:42,279 --> 00:28:43,400
Why not doze a little longer?

403
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:44,960
After all,

404
00:28:45,119 --> 00:28:46,559
no one has come to pay condolences yet.

405
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:48,440
I'm fine.

406
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:56,519
Where are those two?

407
00:28:58,319 --> 00:29:00,039
Perhaps they went somewhere to rest.

408
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,599
You hold the fort here.

409
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:08,279
I'll go check on grandmother.

410
00:29:46,559 --> 00:29:47,960
The doctor added to the prescription

411
00:29:47,960 --> 00:29:49,440
some sedative herbs.

412
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:50,680
Last night,

413
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,759
she finally slept soundly.

414
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:56,000
Otherwise she gets up seven or eight times a night.

415
00:29:56,559 --> 00:29:58,400
After all, she is getting on in years.

416
00:29:58,759 --> 00:30:01,000
It truly makes one worry.

417
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,519
Grandmother said yesterday,

418
00:30:09,079 --> 00:30:10,039
following my late aunt's last wish

419
00:30:10,279 --> 00:30:11,480
to be buried in Tongzhou,

420
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:14,079
