421
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,519
to prepare in advance.

422
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,519
I'm worried her health can't take it.

423
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:20,599
On my behalf,

424
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:22,079
please persuade her well.

425
00:30:23,799 --> 00:30:24,839
You know

426
00:30:24,839 --> 00:30:25,680
Grandmother's temperament,

427
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,119
She can't be persuaded at all.

428
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:28,160
Besides,

429
00:30:28,720 --> 00:30:29,519
going back is good.

430
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,359
Staying here

431
00:30:32,079 --> 00:30:33,559
will only grieve her old heart.

432
00:30:36,599 --> 00:30:37,160
Okay.

433
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:39,960
Then on the road,

434
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,079
take good care of her.

435
00:30:41,559 --> 00:30:42,440
Don't worry.

436
00:30:42,759 --> 00:30:43,480
As for Grandmother's side,

437
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:44,640
I've already arranged everything.

438
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:45,599
Moreover,

439
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,359
Grandmother also said

440
00:30:47,359 --> 00:30:48,319
that I should stay and look after you.

441
00:30:49,039 --> 00:30:50,000
I'm fine.

442
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,559
I also want to stay and take care of you.

443
00:30:52,200 --> 00:30:53,000
I'm really... Be good.

444
00:31:09,079 --> 00:31:09,640
Lord,

445
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,319
