446
00:31:11,759 --> 00:31:12,799
I had someone inquire,

447
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:14,160
and there are all sorts of rumors.

448
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,559
Some say she died of illness,

449
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,000
some say it was that previous concubine

450
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:17,839
who angered her to death,

451
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,400
and others even

452
00:31:19,839 --> 00:31:21,000
say it was suicide.

453
00:31:22,559 --> 00:31:24,079
Have someone find out in detail

454
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,160
what really happened.

455
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:26,359
Best to directly

456
00:31:26,359 --> 00:31:27,200
