474
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:39,880
This isn't miscalculating,

475
00:32:41,279 --> 00:32:42,720
you calculated a bit too clearly.

476
00:32:45,359 --> 00:32:46,359
Even your own funeral rites

477
00:32:46,359 --> 00:32:47,720
and incense oil money are included.

478
00:32:48,559 --> 00:32:50,319
I was never good with figures,

479
00:32:50,559 --> 00:32:51,640
please forgive me, Miss.

480
00:32:52,359 --> 00:32:53,240
Not good at calculation?

481
00:32:54,519 --> 00:32:55,599
You're too modest.

482
00:32:56,759 --> 00:32:58,000
Look at this account you've made,

483
00:32:58,519 --> 00:32:59,440
every penny accounted for,

484
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:00,799
clearly not a beginner's work.

485
00:33:02,960 --> 00:33:04,319
You're an old hand in the Gu household.

486
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:05,559
Originally,

487
00:33:06,119 --> 00:33:07,640
I should give you some face.

488
00:33:08,079 --> 00:33:09,640
But this is no ordinary matter,

489
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:12,480
