490
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,720
a time of mourning for the whole household.

491
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:15,960
Yet you actually thought

492
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:17,319
to skim money from the mansion.

493
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:19,480
Guards.

494
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:20,319
Drag him away.

495
00:33:20,759 --> 00:33:21,519
Twenty strokes of the plank.

496
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:22,599
And throw him out directly.

497
00:33:22,599 --> 00:33:22,920
Yes.

498
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,720
Miss! Miss, spare my life!

499
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,400
Forgive me, Miss!

500
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,400
Miss!

501
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:28,920
Miss!

502
00:33:30,519 --> 00:33:31,079
Miss Gu.

503
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:33,720
Guard Chen.

504
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,880
Mr. Chen Master ordered me

505
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,839
to send some servants and maids

506
00:33:35,839 --> 00:33:36,680
for your use.

507
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:37,880
They are all waiting outside.

508
00:33:38,519 --> 00:33:39,240
Mr. Chen also said

509
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:40,720
He will see you later.

510
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:42,839
Thank you.

511
00:33:58,720 --> 00:33:59,480
I know.

512
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:01,759
You all think

513
00:34:01,759 --> 00:34:03,279
that my first time as a director,

514
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,599
and still an unmarried young lady,

515
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:05,720
that I'm thin-skinned,

516
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:06,960
easy to bully.

517
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:10,199
Then you're quirt wrong.

518
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:12,119
Those who aren't afraid to die,

519
00:34:13,039 --> 00:34:13,920
just come and try me.

520
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:16,119
Those who don't want to work,

521
00:34:16,719 --> 00:34:17,960
come forward early and say so.

522
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,039
Forgive us, Ms. Jinzhao.

523
00:34:21,159 --> 00:34:22,320
Forgive us, Ms. Jinzhao.

524
00:34:22,599 --> 00:34:23,840
Forgive us, Ms. Jinzhao.

525
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:25,480
Forgive us, Ms. Jinzhao.

526
00:34:29,559 --> 00:34:30,039
Thanks.

527
00:34:30,039 --> 00:34:30,639
Let's go, let's go.

528
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:31,760
Mr. Chen.

529
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:32,320
He's here.

530
00:34:33,559 --> 00:34:34,239
I'll take my leave first.

531
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:35,559
How is she?

532
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,400
She seems alright.

533
00:34:38,719 --> 00:34:39,519
All the arrangements,

534
00:34:39,679 --> 00:34:40,519
everything is in perfect order.

535
00:34:41,199 --> 00:34:42,440
The more perfect the order,

536
00:34:42,639 --> 00:34:43,599
the worse it actually is.

537
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,119
Lord Chen, please hold on.

538
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,239
The Lord Chief Councilor

539
00:34:52,239 --> 00:34:53,559
requests you to go to the Wenyuan Pavilion.

540
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:00,480
Go fetch a set of plain mourning clothes

541
00:35:00,639 --> 00:35:01,360
and wait here.

542
00:35:02,159 --> 00:35:02,599
Yes.

543
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,199
The Heir of Lord Changxing,

544
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:10,239
and the Fifth Madam Gu, have come to pay condolences.

545
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:18,239
Given your status,

546
