547
00:37:32,199 --> 00:37:33,679
Did your mother truly die of illness?

548
00:37:44,079 --> 00:37:45,719
Why would Young Lord say such a thing?

549
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:47,599
What do you think?

550
00:37:48,159 --> 00:37:48,840
Others may not know,

551
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:49,800
but how could I not.

552
00:37:51,559 --> 00:37:53,079
Your mother was murdered.

553
