Who did it.

554
00:37:55,199 --> 00:37:56,159
I'll help you kill him.

555
00:38:05,559 --> 00:38:06,360
Good boy.

556
00:38:07,039 --> 00:38:07,880
I heard that

557
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,760
you've been handling all the funeral affairs.

558
00:38:10,079 --> 00:38:11,280
Don't wear yourself out.

559
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,000
My fourth sister-in-law's spirit in heaven,

560
00:38:13,119 --> 00:38:13,800
seeing you and Jinrong

561
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,760
being so filial,

562
00:38:15,079 --> 00:38:16,079
will surely be comforted.

563
00:38:17,519 --> 00:38:18,599
Thank you, Fifth Aunt.

564
00:38:20,239 --> 00:38:21,199
Then you carry on.

565
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:24,880
Gu Jinzhao, head back first.

566
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,039
Do you know

567
00:38:33,039 --> 00:38:33,880
what you're doing.

568
00:38:34,159 --> 00:38:35,519
The dignified Heir of a Marquis's house,

569
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:36,559
kowtowing before the coffin

570
00:38:36,559 --> 00:38:37,519
