573
00:38:40,519 --> 00:38:41,400
what a scandal!

574
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,320
I really regret

575
00:38:43,559 --> 00:38:45,000
ever being soft-hearted and bringing you here.

576
00:38:45,639 --> 00:38:46,760
You, soft-hearted?

577
00:38:47,519 --> 00:38:49,320
You just wanted to use this chance to remind me,

578
00:38:49,719 --> 00:38:51,440
to make me give up on Gu Jinzhao.

579
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:53,360
Even so,

580
00:38:53,559 --> 00:38:54,599
I'm doing it for your own good,

581
00:38:54,719 --> 00:38:55,360
for the Marquis's house.

582
00:38:56,079 --> 00:38:57,719
Do you think I enjoy being the villain

583
00:38:57,719 --> 00:38:58,880
who breaks up loving couples?

584
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,880
If only I were a man,

585
00:39:02,199 --> 00:39:03,119
I could establish my own household,

586
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,480
I could contribute to the Marquis's house.

587
00:39:04,639 --> 00:39:05,760
Would I need to force you?

588
00:39:06,239 --> 00:39:07,599
You could marry whomever you wish.

589
00:39:09,119 --> 00:39:10,320
Unfortunately I am not.

590
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:11,880
I can only support my husband

591
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,880
and educate my children in another family,

592
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,559
watching family's prospects in anxious helplessness.

593
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:49,480
If I had known,

594
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:51,039
you loved degrading yourself this much,

595
00:39:51,719 --> 00:39:52,719
back then I should have just let you

596
00:39:52,719 --> 00:39:53,559
die and be done with it.

597
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:55,400
Why bother to save you.

598
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:59,400
Mrs. Gu didn't die of illness.

599
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:01,360
Obviously.

600
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:04,400
I asked Jinzhao who did it,

601
00:40:05,079 --> 00:40:05,880
she refused to say.

602
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,840
It's not that she refuses to say,

603
00:40:08,119 --> 00:40:09,400
it's that she can't.

604
00:40:10,199 --> 00:40:10,960
Mrs. Gu

605
00:40:11,039 --> 00:40:12,320
was likely not murdered,

606
00:40:13,159 --> 00:40:14,480
but rather, took her own life.

607
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,360
How do you know.

608
00:40:21,679 --> 00:40:23,320
Didn't I say that last time.

609
00:40:26,559 --> 00:40:27,559
Mrs. Gu,

610
00:40:29,079 --> 00:40:30,280
her liver qi was stagnant,

611
00:40:30,519 --> 00:40:31,679
melancholy turned to illness.

612
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,039
For such a person,

613
00:40:34,199 --> 00:40:35,599
if the knot in their heart cannot be untied,

614
00:40:36,639 --> 00:40:37,639
nine times out of ten,

615
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,440
they end their own life.

616
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:42,760
It's just a pity for this Miss Gu,

617
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:45,519
losing her own mother before she's even married,

618
00:40:46,079 --> 00:40:47,079
it's also quite troublesome.

619
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,280
I'll take care of her.

620
00:40:53,039 --> 00:40:54,840
I know what you're thinking.

621
00:40:55,119 --> 00:40:56,199
You're overthinking it.

622
00:40:56,639 --> 00:40:58,000
You can't take care of her.

623
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:00,039
Even you don't believe in me.

624
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,400
It's not that I don't believe you.

625
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,280
In this world,

626
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:05,400
if you cannot stand firm,

627
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:07,480
you can't look after anyone.

628
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,840
With your physical condition alone,

629
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:12,360
no matter how great my medical skill,

630
00:41:12,679 --> 00:41:13,639
I could never heal you enough

631
00:41:13,639 --> 00:41:15,360
to kill enemies and earn merit on the battlefield.

632
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:17,559
If you can't stand firm,

633
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,599
this Marquis's house cannot stand firm.

634
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,639
If the Marquis's house cannot stand firm,

635
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,079
Your marriage

636
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,639
will not be your own decision.

637
00:41:26,519 --> 00:41:28,000
It's all fate.

638
00:41:29,119 --> 00:41:30,039
Others believe in fate,

639
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:31,320
I refuse to believe.

640
00:41:32,199 --> 00:41:33,000
Back then, everyone

641
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,119
said my heart condition was severe,

642
00:41:34,119 --> 00:41:35,079
that I wouldn't live past ten.

643
00:41:35,559 --> 00:41:36,239
But didn't you still

644
00:41:36,239 --> 00:41:37,199
pull me back from the brink.

645
00:41:38,719 --> 00:41:39,639
I just don't believe

646
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:41,360
that only military merit can keep one standing firm.

647
00:41:42,239 --> 00:41:43,239
In this world,

648
00:41:43,599 --> 00:41:44,480
there must be a path

649
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,599
outside of military merit.

650
00:41:51,679 --> 00:41:53,079
My mother, upon hearing of Mrs. Gu's

651
00:41:53,079 --> 00:41:54,000
sudden passing,

652
00:41:54,559 --> 00:41:55,519
was deeply saddened.

653
00:41:56,159 --> 00:41:56,920
She specially ordered me

654
00:41:57,920 --> 00:41:59,199
to come here in her stead to pay condolences.

655
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:02,119
The Madam Ji is truly one who cherishes old ties.

656
00:42:03,559 --> 00:42:04,199
Lord Chen.

657
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,079
My younger brother,

658
00:42:06,159 --> 00:42:07,199
stricken by this sudden tragedy,

659
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:08,440
has fallen gravely ill and is bedridden.

660
00:42:08,639 --> 00:42:09,159
Otherwise,

661
00:42:09,239 --> 00:42:10,079
he certainly would have come to greet you.

662
00:42:10,159 --> 00:42:10,840
It's quite alright.
